#. type: Plain text
#: source/securing_apps/topics/saml/mod-auth-mellon.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "The https://github.com/UNINETT/mod_auth_mellon[mod_auth_mellon] module is an Apache HTTPD plugin for SAML. If your language/environment supports using Apache HTTPD as a proxy, then you can use mod_auth_mellon to secure your web application with SAML. For more details on this module see the _mod_auth_mellon_ Github repo.\n"
